{"tid":134307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"媽媽驚見兒子伴7歲童屍　斬首碎屍仲食緊","createTime":"2017-02-25T11:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T06:17:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45b83201f53bfa61cddbbc0355eee6db23960c15","tid":134307,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>【食童屍肉】媽媽驚見兒子伴7歲童屍 斬首碎屍仲食緊<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170224/56346527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170224%2F56346527&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXckzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=0fde6621\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170224%2F56346527&h=c7ddd568\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170224/56346527</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n印度北方邦一名媽媽揭發其成年兒子將一名7歲男童碎屍後，將屍體吃掉，場面極度恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487881317_27df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487881317_27df.jpg&h=6074e1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20多歲的米揚（Nazim Miyan）被母親發現在一間空屋內，現場血跡斑斑，米揚身旁有一具童屍，身首異處，頸、手臂、雙腿被斬碎，腹部皮膚被剝去，內臟散滿一地。據報死者本與朋友玩耍，被米揚誘拐並殘殺。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場後拘捕米揚，他並無反抗，但被帶走期間遭憤怒村民毆打。警方在案發現場撿獲一把刀和一個鏟，相信是兇器。米揚被落案控謀殺和拐帶兒童，警方指他接受問話時語無倫次。幾百名村民在警局外聚集，要求處死米揚。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"194753f55fd7b374f7eb4d138db73120da5142b3","tid":134307,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69686a1758649923e3f72b1acc1448ba39152162","tid":134307,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:22:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"2c32c9b740be0032fa0ad9d37209697f4c268f9a","tid":134307,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T06:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}